When aligning sequences, LASTZ excludes soft-masked bases from its \seed" stage but reintroduces them in later stages, when alignments of un- masked sequence can be extended into soft-masked regions (see webpage: http://www.bx.psu.edu/miller_lab/dist/README.lastz-1.02.00/README.
